          <p style={{ fontSize: 15, color: colors.primary, marginBottom: 20, fontWeight: 500, lineHeight: 1.6 }}>
            <strong>Referring a patient?</strong> We work with discharge planners, social workers, and specialist teams across the GTA.
          </p>
          <Link href="/referral-form/" className="arc-btn-primary">
            Submit a Professional Referral →
